sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Consumidor as Consumidore/Aplicación
    participant API as API Pago Préstamo <br> Epica 2267: PagoPrestamo <br> HU 56993:  POST -  /loan-payment/v1/execution
    participant CL as Caché Local
    participant Lambda as Lambda de parámetros
    participant Lib as Librería Pipeline (ConfigMap)
    participant retriveTransactionDetails as API Consulta Detalles Cuenta <br> HU 3319 <br> GET: /loans-and-deposits/customer-account-retrieves/v1/product/accountIdentification/retrieve-transaction-details
    participant retrieveLoan as API Consulta Detalles Préstamo <br> HU 3239 <br> GET: /loans-and-deposits/loan-retrieves/v1/product/loanReference/retrieve
    participant tengo as API Retiro Efectivo Tengo <br> HU 57119 <br> POST: /loans-and-deposits/loan-admin/v1/initiate-transaction
    participant transfer1 as API Transferencia Entre Cuentas Misma Moneda <br> HU 55274 <br> POST: /payments/payment-execution-transfer/v1/initiate-transfers-between-accounts
    participant transfer2 as API Transferencia Entre Cuentas Credito <br> HU 4368 <br> POST: /payments/payment-execution-transfer/v1/payment-execution-apply
    participant transfer3 as API Transferencia Entre Cuentas <br> HU 7837 <br> POST: /payments/payment-execution-admin/v1/initiate-transfers-between-accounts
    participant loanPayment as API Ejectuar Pago Prestamo HN <br> HU 5576:  POST: /payments/payment-execution-maintenance/v1/execute-loan-repayment
    participant reverse as API Reverse Loan Payment <br> HU 33776:  POST: /loan-payment-mgmt/v1/reverse-transaction
    participant cashCreditAccount as API Ejectuar Crédito Cuenta Contable <br> HU 57003:  POST: /loans-and-deposits/loan-admin/v1/execute-repayment
    participant cheque as API Depósito Cheque <br> HU 57060:  POST: /loans-and-deposits/current-account-mgmt/v1/initiate-check-deposit
    participant Errors as Control de Errores <br> Librería de mapeo de errores
    
    Note over Consumidor, Errors: Flujo Honduras (HN01) - Realizar Pago Préstamo

    Consumidor->>API: REST Request
    Note right of Consumidor: body: <br> loanId, <br> paymentAmount, <br> paymentType, <br> accountNumber, <br> chequeNumber <br> bankCode, <br> interfaceReferenceNumber, <br> debitCreditIndicator, <br> transactionReferenceBC, <br> currencyCode

    API->>API: Validar Request
    Note over API: Valida campos obligatorios según contrato OpenAPI 

    API->>API: Validación exitosa

    alt Consulta parametros en caché local

        API->>CL: Consultar parámetros Lambda Parámetros caché local
        Note right of API: Domain: "LOAN_PAYMENT" <br> name: "EXECUTION" <br> country: XRS 

        CL->>API: Obtiene parámetros Lambda Parámetros Cahé Local
        Note left of CL: Obtiene parámetros de regionalización y negocio

    else Consulta  parametros en Lambda Parámetros / Parameter Store

        API->>Lambda: Consultar parámetros lambda parámetros
        Note right of API: Domain: "LOAN_PAYMENT" <br> name: "EXECUTION" <br> country: XRS 

        Lambda->>API: Obtiene parámetros Lambda Parámetros
        Note left of Lambda: Obtiene parámetros de regionalización y negocio

        API->>CL: Guarda parámetros lambda Parámetros en caché local
        Note right of API: value.param-name 

    end

    API->>API: Validar Servicio Regional
    Note over API: Usando parámetros de regionalización obtenidos

    API->>API: Validación Regional Exitosa
    Note over API: Servicio habilitado para HN01 

    API->>API: Evaluar request.paymentType

    alt If request.paymentType == "ACCOUNT_DEBIT" 
        rect rgb(235, 243, 214)
        Note over API, Errors: Flujo para paymentType == "ACCOUNT_DEBIT" 
            alt if accountNumber == vacío

                API->> Errors: Mapear código de error

                Errors ->> API: Retorna código mapeado

                API->> Consumidor: Retorna error
                Note left of API: HTTP 400: accountNumber debe ser diferente de vacío

            else If accountNumber != vacío
                
                Note over API, retrieveLoan: Consumo en paralelo a las APIs de producto retriveTransactionDetails y retrieveLoan

                API->>API: Constrye Request API retriveTransactionDetails
                Note over API: pathParam: <br> accountIdentification = request.accountNumber

                API->>retriveTransactionDetails: Consume API Producto retriveTransactionDetails
                Note right of API: pathParam: <br> accountIdentification

                retriveTransactionDetails->>API: Response API Producto retriveTransactionDetails
                Note left of retriveTransactionDetails: responseBody: <br>  accountCurrency <br> ++ Campos

                API->>API: Constrye Request API retrieveLoan
                Note over API: pathParam: <br> loanReference = request.loanId

                API->>retrieveLoan: Consume API Producto retrieveLoan
                Note right of API: pathParam: <br> loanReference

                retrieveLoan->>API: Response API Producto retrieveLoan
                Note left of retrieveLoan: responseBody: <br>  currency <br> ++ Campos
                
                API->>API: Evaluar Response APIs retriveTransactionDetails y retrieveLoan

                alt If Response.retriveTransactionDetails or Response.retrieveLoan HTTP CODE != 200 

                    API->> Errors: Mapear código de error

                    Errors ->> API: Retorna código mapeado

                    API->> Consumidor: Retorna error
                    Note left of API: HTTP 422: No existe información para la cuenta y el préstamo

                else If response.retriveTransactionDetails and response.retrieveLoan HTTP CODE == 200 (Los dos response deben ser exitosos)
                    rect rgb(242, 242, 242)
                    Note over API, transfer3: Ejecutar la trasnferencia entre cuentas

                        alt If request.transactionReferenceBC != Vacío (Significa que la transacción viene de un corresponsal bancario)

                            API->>API: Constrye Request API inititateTransactionTengo
                            Note over API: body: <br> transactionType = lamda.T24T133.TXNTYPELOANPYMT, <br> debitAccountNumber = request.accountNumber, <br> debitCurrencyCode = request.currencyCode, <br> debitAmount = paymentAmount, <br> creditAccountNumber = lambda.T24T134.HNLCREDITACCTNO, <br> groupAttribute = lamda.paymentGroupAttribute, <br> paymentDetailsDescription = request.loanId, <br> tengoReference = request.transactionReferenceBC

                            API->>tengo: Consume API Producto inititateTransactionTengo
                            Note right of API: body: <br> transactionType, <br> debitAccountNumber, <br> debitCurrencyCode, <br> debitAmount, <br> creditAccountNumber, <br> groupAttribute, <br> paymentDetailsDescription, <br> tengoReference

                            tengo->>API: Response API Producto inititateTransactionTengo
                            Note left of tengo: responseBody: <br>  transactionReference <br> ++ Campos

                            API->>API: Asigna Variables
                            Note over API: $transactionReference = response.transactionReference

                        else If response.retriveTransactionDetails.accountCurrency == response.retrieveLoan.currency 

                            API->>API: Constrye Request API trasnferBetweemAccounsSameCurrency
                            Note over API: body: <br> paymentTransactionType = lamda.T24T133.TXNTYPELOANPYMT, <br> debtorAccountReference = request.accountNumber , <br> currencyCode = request.currencyCode, <br> paymentAmount = request.paymentAmount, <br> creditorAccountReference = lambda.T24T134.HNLCREDITACCTNO, <br> businessUnitReference = lambda.orderingBank <br> transactionDescription = concat("PTM-", request.loanId)

                            API->>transfer1: Consume API Producto trasnferBetweemAccounsSameCurrency
                            Note right of API: body: <br> paymentTransactionType, <br> debtorAccountReference, <br> currencyCode, <br> paymentAmount, <br> creditorAccountReference, <br> businessUnitReference <br> transactionDescription

                            transfer1->>API: Response API Producto trasnferBetweemAccounsSameCurrency
                            Note left of transfer1: responseBody: <br> transactionReference <br> ++ Campos

                            API->>API: Asigna Variables
                            Note over API: $transactionReference = response.transactionReference 

                        else If request.debitCreditIndicator == "CREDIT"

                            API->>API: Constrye Request API trasnferCredit
                            Note over API: body: paymentTransactionType = lamda.T24T133.TXNTYPELOANPYMT <br>  debtorAccountReference = request.accountNumber, <br> creditorAccountReference = lambda.T24T134.HNLCREDITACCTNO, <br> creditorAmount = request.paymentAmount

                            API->>transfer2: Consume API Producto trasnferCredit
                            Note right of API: body: <br> paymentTransactionType, <br> debtorAccountReference, <br> creditorAccountReference, <br> creditorAmount

                            transfer2->>API: Response API Producto trasnferCredit
                            Note left of transfer2: responseBody: <br>  transactionReference <br> ++ Campos

                            API->>API: Asigna Variables
                            Note over API: $transactionReference = response.transactionReference 

                        else

                            API->>API: Constrye Request API trasnferAccount
                            Note over API: body: transactionType = lamda.T24T133.TXNTYPELOANPYMT <br>  debitAccountReference = request.accountNumber, <br> creditAccountReference = lambda.T24T134.HNLCREDITACCTNO, <br> debitAmount = request.paymentAmount

                            API->>transfer3: Consume API Producto trasnferAccount
                            Note right of API: body: <br> paymentTransactionType, <br> debitAccountReference, <br> creditAccountReference, <br> debitAmount

                            transfer3->>API: Response API Producto trasnferAccount
                            Note left of transfer3: responseBody: <br>  transactionReference <br> ++ Campos

                            API->>API: Asigna Variables
                            Note over API: $transactionReference = response.transactionReference 

                        end

                    end 

                    API->>API: Evaluar Response APIs Trasnferencia

                    alt If response APIs transferencia != HTTP CODE 200

                        API->> Errors: Mapear código de error

                        Errors ->> API: Retorna código mapeado

                        API->> Consumidor: Retorna error
                        Note left of API: Se mapea código de error de la API de producto consumida para la transferencia

                    else 

                        alt If request.transactionReferenceBC != Vacío (Significa que la transacción viene de un corresponsal bancario)

                            API->>API: Constrye Request API executeLoanPayment
                            Note over API: body: <br> loanId = request.loanId, <br> paymentAmount = request.paymentAmount, <br> paymentType = request.paymentType, <br> accountNumber = request.accountNumber, <br> interfaceReferenceNumber = request.interfaceReferenceNumber, <br> transactionReference = $transactionReference, <br> transactionReferenceBC = request.transactionReferenceBC, <br> paymentDescription = lambda.desciption-cb

                            API->>loanPayment: Consume API Producto executeLoanPayment
                            Note right of API: body: <br> loanId, <br> paymentAmount, <br> paymentType, <br> accountNumber, <br> interfaceReferenceNumber, <br> transactionReference, <br> transactionReferenceBC, <br> paymentDescription

                            loanPayment->>API: Response API Producto executeLoanPayment
                            Note left of loanPayment: responseBody: <br>  paymentExecutionDateTime, installmentReference <br> ++ Campos

                            alt If response API executeLoanPayment != HTTP CODE 200

                                API->>API: Constrye Request API reverseTransaction
                                Note over API: body: <br> transactionReference = $transactionReference <br> transactionType = " "

                                API->>reverse: Consume API Producto reverseTransaction
                                Note right of API: body: transactionReference, <br> transactionType

                                reverse->>API: Response API Producto reverseTransaction
                                Note left of reverse: responseBody: <br>  transactionDate
                                
                                API->> Errors: Mapear código de error

                                Errors ->> API: Retorna código mapeado

                                API->> Consumidor: Retorna error
                                Note left of API: Se mapea código de error de la API de producto executeLoanPayment
                            
                            else If response API executeLoanPayment == HTTP CODE 200

                                API->>API: Construye response API
                                Note over API: Mapeo uno a uno con los campos response API Prod executeLoanPayment

                                API->>Consumidor: Response Exitoso
                                Note left of API: HTTP 200: Response Body 

                            end

                        else If request.transactionReferenceBC == Vacío o no presente (Significa que la transacción viene de un canal diferente a corresponsal bancario)
                            
                            API->>API: Constrye Request API executeLoanPayment
                            Note over API: body: <br> loanId = request.loanId, <br> paymentAmount = request.paymentAmount, <br> accountNumber = request.accountNumber, <br> interfaceReferenceNumber = request.interfaceReferenceNumber, <br> transactionReference = $transactionReference

                            API->>loanPayment: Consume API Producto executeLoanPayment
                            Note right of API: body: <br> loanId, <br> paymentAmount, <br> paymentType, <br> accountNumber, <br> interfaceReferenceNumber, <br> transactionReference, <br> transactionReferenceBC, <br> paymentDescription

                            loanPayment->>API: Response API Producto executeLoanPayment
                            Note left of loanPayment: responseBody: <br>  paymentExecutionDateTime, installmentReference <br> ++ Campos

                            API->>API: Evaluar Response API executeLoanPayment

                            alt If response API executeLoanPayment != HTTP CODE 200

                                API->>API: Constrye Request API reverseTransaction
                                Note over API: body: <br> transactionReference = $transactionReference <br> transactionType = " "

                                API->>reverse: Consume API Producto reverseTransaction
                                Note right of API: body: transactionReference, <br> transactionType

                                reverse->>API: Response API Producto reverseTransaction
                                Note left of reverse: responseBody: <br>  transactionDate

                                API->> Errors: Mapear código de error

                                Errors ->> API: Retorna código mapeado

                                API->> Consumidor: Retorna error
                                Note left of API: Se mapea código de error de la API de producto executeLoanPayment
                             
                            else If response API executeLoanPayment == HTTP CODE 200

                                API->>API: Construye response API
                                Note over API: Mapeo uno a uno con los campos response API Prod executeLoanPayment

                                API->>Consumidor: Response Exitoso
                                Note left of API: HTTP 200: Response Body 

                            end

                        end 
                    
                    end

                end

            end

        end
    end 

    alt If request.paymentType == "CASH" 
        rect rgb(243, 238, 214)
        Note over API, Errors: Flujo para paymentType == "CASH"

            API->>API: Constrye Request API retrieveLoan
            Note over API: pathParam: <br> loanReference = request.loanId

            API->>retrieveLoan: Consume API Producto retrieveLoan
            Note right of API: pathParam: <br> loanReference

            retrieveLoan->>API: Response API Producto retrieveLoan
            Note left of retrieveLoan: responseBody: <br>  currency
            
            API->>API: Evaluar Response API retrieveLoan

            alt If  Response.retrieveLoan HTTP CODE != 200 

                API->> Errors: Mapear código de error

                Errors ->> API: Retorna código mapeado

                API->> Consumidor: Retorna error
                Note left of API: Se mapea código de error de la API de producto retrieveLoan

            else If response.retrieveLoan HTTP CODE == 200 

                API->>API: Constrye Request API cashCreditAccount
                Note over API: body: <br> currencyCode = request.currencyCode, <br> paymentAmount = request.paymentAmount, <br> authorizationsNumber = lambda.noOfAuth, <br> accountGroup = lambda.accountGroup, <br> accountMultiple = lambda.accountMultiple

                API->>cashCreditAccount: Consume API Producto cashCreditAccount
                Note right of API: body: <br> currencyCode, <br> paymentAmount, <br> authorizationsNumber, <br> accountGroup, <br> accountMultiple

                cashCreditAccount->>API: Response API Producto cashCreditAccount
                Note left of cashCreditAccount: responseBody: <br> loanRepaymentTransactionId, <br> ++ Campos
                
                API->>API: Evaluar Response API cashCreditAccount
                
                alt If  Response.cashCreditAccount HTTP CODE != 200 

                    API->> Errors: Mapear código de error

                    Errors ->> API: Retorna código mapeado

                    API->> Consumidor: Retorna error
                    Note left of API: Se mapea código de error de la API de producto cashCreditAccount

                else If response.cashCreditAccount HTTP CODE == 200 

                    API->>API: Constrye Request API executeLoanPayment
                    Note over API: body: <br> loanId = request.loanId, <br> paymentAmount = request.paymentAmount, <br> accountNumber = request.accountNumber, <br> interfaceReferenceNumber = request.interfaceReferenceNumber, <br> transactionReference = responseCashCreditAccount.loanRepaymentTransactionId

                    API->>loanPayment: Consume API Producto executeLoanPayment
                    Note right of API: body: <br> loanId, <br> paymentAmount, <br> accountNumber, <br> interfaceReferenceNumber, <br> transactionReference

                    loanPayment->>API: Response API Producto executeLoanPayment
                    Note left of loanPayment: responseBody: <br>  paymentExecutionDateTime, installmentReference <br> ++ Campos

                    API->>API: Evaluar Response API executeLoanPayment

                    alt If response API executeLoanPayment != HTTP CODE 200

                        API->>API: Constrye Request API reverseTransaction
                        Note over API: body: <br> transactionReference = $transactionReference <br> transactionType = " "

                        API->>reverse: Consume API Producto reverseTransaction
                        Note right of API: body: transactionReference, <br> transactionType

                        reverse->>API: Response API Producto reverseTransaction
                        Note left of reverse: responseBody: <br>  transactionDate

                        API->> Errors: Mapear código de error

                        Errors ->> API: Retorna código mapeado

                        API->> Consumidor: Retorna error
                        Note left of API: Se mapea código de error de la API de producto executeLoanPayment
                    
                    else

                        API->>API: Construye response API
                        Note over API: Mapeo uno a uno con los campos response API Prod executeLoanPayment

                        API->>Consumidor: Response Exitoso
                        Note left of API: HTTP 200: Response Body 

                    end

                end

            end

        end

    end

    alt If request.paymentType == "OTHER_BANK_CHEQUE" 
        rect rgb(233, 228, 248)
        Note over API, Errors: Flujo para paymentType == "OTHER_BANK_CHEQUE"

            API->>API: Constrye Request API retrieveLoan
            Note over API: pathParam: <br> loanReference = request.loanId

            API->>retrieveLoan: Consume API Producto retrieveLoan
            Note right of API: pathParam: <br> loanReference

            retrieveLoan->>API: Response API Producto retrieveLoan
            Note left of retrieveLoan: responseBody: <br>  currency
            
            API->>API: Evaluar Response API retrieveLoan

            alt If  Response.retrieveLoan HTTP CODE != 200 

                API->> Errors: Mapear código de error

                Errors ->> API: Retorna código mapeado

                API->> Consumidor: Retorna error
                Note left of API: Se mapea código de error de la API de producto retrieveLoan

            else If response.retrieveLoan HTTP CODE == 200 

                API->>API: Constrye Request API checkDeposit
                Note over API: body: <br> chequeNumber = request.chequeNumber, <br> bankCode = request.bankCode, <br> loanCurrency = request.currencyCode, <br> paymentAmount = request.paymentAmount, <br> noOfAuth = lambda.chequeNoOfAuth, <br> groupAttribute = lambda.groupAttribute, <br> multiGroupAttribute = lambda.multiGroupAttribute, <br> transactionReference = lambda.transaction

                API->>cheque: Consume API Producto checkDeposit
                Note right of API: body: <br> chequeNumber, <br> bankCode, <br> loanCurrency, <br> paymentAmount, <br> noOfAuth, <br> groupAttribute, <br> multiGroupAttribute, <br> transactionReference

                cheque->>API: Response API Producto checkDeposit
                Note left of cheque: responseBody: <br> transactionReference, <br> ++ Campos
                
                API->>API: Evaluar Response API checkDeposit
                
                alt If  Response.checkDeposit HTTP CODE != 200 

                    API->> Errors: Mapear código de error

                    Errors ->> API: Retorna código mapeado

                    API->> Consumidor: Retorna error
                    Note left of API: Se mapea código de error de la API de producto checkDeposit

                else If response.checkDeposit HTTP CODE == 200 

                    API->>API: Constrye Request API executeLoanPayment
                    Note over API: body: <br> loanId = request.loanId, <br> paymentAmount = request.paymentAmount, <br> accountNumber = request.accountNumber, <br> interfaceReferenceNumber = request.interfaceReferenceNumber, <br> transactionReference = responseCheckDeposit.transactionReference

                    API->>loanPayment: Consume API Producto executeLoanPayment
                    Note right of API: body: <br> loanId, <br> paymentAmount, <br> accountNumber, <br> interfaceReferenceNumber, <br> transactionReference

                    loanPayment->>API: Response API Producto executeLoanPayment
                    Note left of loanPayment: responseBody: <br>  paymentExecutionDateTime, installmentReference <br> ++ Campos

                    API->>API: Evaluar Response API executeLoanPayment

                    alt If response API executeLoanPayment != HTTP CODE 200

                        API->>API: Constrye Request API reverseTransaction
                        Note over API: body: <br> transactionReference = $transactionReference <br> transactionType = " "

                        API->>reverse: Consume API Producto reverseTransaction
                        Note right of API: body: transactionReference, <br> transactionType

                        reverse->>API: Response API Producto reverseTransaction
                        Note left of reverse: responseBody: <br>  transactionDate

                        API->> Errors: Mapear código de error

                        Errors ->> API: Retorna código mapeado

                        API->> Consumidor: Retorna error
                        Note left of API: Se mapea código de error de la API de producto executeLoanPayment
                    
                    else

                        API->>API: Construye response API
                        Note over API: Mapeo uno a uno con los campos response API Prod executeLoanPayment

                        API->>Consumidor: Response Exitoso
                        Note left of API: HTTP 200: Response Body 

                    end

                end

            end

        end

    end

    Note over Consumidor, Errors: Flujo Alternativo - Error
    activate API
    alt Exception occurs
        note over Errors: Error Library Handler
        activate Errors
            API->> Errors: Mapear código de error
            Errors ->> API: Retorna código mapeado
        deactivate Errors
        activate Consumidor
            API-->> Consumidor: Retorna error
        deactivate Consumidor
        Note over Consumidor,Errors: Diagrama guía de manejo de errores <br> http://bit.ly/4rpKVIU
    end
    deactivate API